criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Female;

          -  English speaking;

          -  Currently reporting heavy drinking;

          -  Identifies as a sexual minority woman.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Unwilling or unable to provide informed consent;

          -  Low literacy (i.e., reporting they "often" or "always" need someone to read
             instructions, pamphlets, or other written material from a doctor or pharmacy to them)

          -  Women who report intention to move away during study period.

          -  Active suicidality.
